quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Abaphumeleleyo ngokwenene ngamakholwa
  23,2,Abo benza iSalâh yabo ngokuzithobileyo
  23,3,Nabo bazikhwebulayo kwintetho ekukungcola
  23,4,Nabo bahlawula iZakâh (rhoqo)
  23,5,Nabo balondoloza iindawo zabo ezinqabileyo ekungcoleni
  23,6,"Ngaphandle kwakubafazi babo okanye kwabo izandla zabo zokunene zibabambileyo, kuba ngenene bona abayi kubekwa tyala"
  23,7,"Kodwa lowo ufuna okungaphaya kunoko, abanjalo ke ngabagabadeli"
  23,8,Ke bona abo bathembakalayo kwizithembiso zabo nakoko bakugcinisiweyo
  23,9,Nabo balondoloza iiSalâh zabo (ngononophelo olungqongqo)
  23,10,Aba ke ngabona zindlalifa zokwenyani
  23,11,Abaza kuyidla ilifa iFirdaws (iPaladesi). Bona baya kuhlala apho ngonaphakade
  23,12,Kananjalo inene Thina Samdala umntu ngengcucu yodongwe
  23,13,Emva koko Sambeka eliqabaza lembewu yomntu kwindawo ekhuselekileyo (isibeleko somfazi)
  23,14,"Saza emva koko Senza iqabaza (elo) lembewu yomntu laba lihlwili elinamathelayo. Saphinda Senza iqabaza lembewu yomntu laba ligaqa (lesihlunu), Saza Senza egaqeni (elo) amathambo; Saza Sawagquma amathambo ngenyama; Saphinda Samphuhlisa waba sesinye isidalwa. Ngoko ke Usikelelekile uAllâh, Ongoyena Mdali Ugqibeleleyo kubadali"
  23,15,Ukanti inene emva koko nisaza kufa
  23,16,"Kananjalo inene nina, ngoMhla woVuko, niza kuvuswa"
  23,17,"Yaye Sidale phezu kwenu amazulu asixhenxe, ukanti aSizanga Thina Singabi nalwazi ngendalo (yeThu)"
  23,18,"Ke kaloku Sithumele imvula phantsi isuka esibhakabhakeni ingomlinganiselo ometiweyo, ize ihlale emhlabeni. Kanti ke Siyakwazi nokuyithabatha imke"
  23,19,Kananjalo Sinenzele ngayo imiyezo yemithi yesundu nezidiliya ezineziqhamo ezininzi enizityayo
  23,20,Kananjalo (Sinihlumisele) umthi ophuma kwintaba yeSinayi ovelisa ioli nokudla (umnquma) enikutyayo
  23,21,"Inene kuni ezilwanyaneni zemfuyo kukho isifundo (kuzo). Sinipha ukuba nisele koko kuvela eziswini zazo, yaye okwenu kuzo apho zizinto ezininzi eziyinzuzo kuni ukanti kwakuzo apho niyadla"
  23,22,Ke kaloku apho ngazo nangeenqanawa niyathwalwa